{"tid":850324,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高鐵集運　強國人一車車湧港：香港是後花園　我會經常來","createTime":"2018-10-06T11:31:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-06T11:39:22.000Z","uid":47714,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"04ece01fff6ae699cf79c1359dc546406c36781d","tid":850324,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T11:31:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20181005/628698\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20181005%2F628698&d=o4wvVtgZmRjIJ0dfGq4TapZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=dc492e75\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20181005%2F628698&h=85f4fa53\" target=\"_blank\">https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20181005/628698</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20181006111439if_/https://scontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t39.2147-6/c0.10.540.282/p540x282/43004556_553336465107009_8958629217642217472_n.jpg?_nc_cat=109&amp;oh=2d7097c619389a9729803ddd62bd3c87&amp;oe=5C1F910E\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20181006111439if_%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft39.2147-6%2Fc0.10.540.282%2Fp540x282%2F43004556_553336465107009_8958629217642217472_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D109%26oh%3D2d7097c619389a9729803ddd62bd3c87%26oe%3D5C1F910E&h=bc308f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://video.next.hk/mcp/encode/2018/10/04/3707053/20181005_news_golden_carol_w.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvideo.next.hk%2Fmcp%2Fencode%2F2018%2F10%2F04%2F3707053%2F20181005_news_golden_carol_w.mp4&d=o4wvVtgZmRjIJ0dfGq4TapZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=44234f32\" target=\"_blank\">https://video.next.hk/mcp/encode/2018/10/04/3707053/20181005_news_golden_carol_w.mp4</a><br />\n<br />\n高鐵香港段通車後，迎來首個十一黃金周，客量一度達7.8萬人次，惟仍未達政府早前預測的八萬人次。黃金周期間，高鐵西九站內人頭湧湧，售票處外有不少內地遊客排隊，附近的五星級酒店「香港W酒店」及「香港麗思卡爾頓酒店」亦不時有內地遊客出入。依站內觀察，高鐵站內大部分都是內地人，香港人只佔少數。<br />\n<br />\n來自深圳的李先生表示，得知高鐵開通後特意試搭。他從深圳北站上車，車程約二十分鐘，認為快捷方便。黃金周期間，酒店房價都會有所提高，李先生表示他以港幣四千元一晚的價錢住在四季酒店，覺得已算便宜：「還好，才四千多元一晚，因為我們訂得早。」<br />\n<br />\n李先生表示，高鐵開通增加其來港意慾：「因為它就像我們的後花園一樣，在整個珠三角，沒有一個城市能比得上香港的服務、美食和購物。以後想來就來，因為隨著這麼方便的高鐵開通以後，我們曾經要做的<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>訪港計劃是不需要了</strong></span>，因為隨時可以買到票就可以走，不像以前我們還要計劃『十一』、『五一』這樣。」內地遊客郭先生亦表示高鐵很方便，但因為大部分時間也在穿過山洞，看不到風景，感覺比較像乘地鐵。"},{"pid":"08128785674e07faf6fc5a4aa6aaa43713d82421","tid":850324,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T11:39:22.000Z","msg":"深圳是後花國"}]}